---
// Testimonio destacado sobre fondo charcoal
---

<section class="testimonio" id="impacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
    <div class="quote">
      Vine a un colegio sin esperanza,<br>
      salí con una nueva vida en Cristo.<br>
      <span class="highlight">LUZ cambió mi futuro.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="attribution">
      <div class="avatar">M</div>
      <div class="who">
        <div class="name">María, 16 años</div>
        <div class="role">Estudiante · Colegio en Heredia</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="badge-wrap">
      <span class="pendiente-badge dark">Testimonio placeholder · pendiente real</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonio {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--on-dark);
    padding: 120px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .testimonio::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    left: -100px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(252,211,77,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .quote-mark {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: var(--yellow);
    line-height: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .quote {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 38px);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--on-dark);
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .highlight { color: var(--yellow); }
  .attribution {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--yellow);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .who { text-align: left; }
  .who .name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; color: var(--on-dark); }
  .who .role { font-size: 13px; color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: 2px; }

  .badge-wrap { margin-top: 32px; }
  .pendiente-badge.dark {
    background: rgba(252,211,77,0.12);
    color: var(--yellow);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .testimonio { padding: 80px 0; }
  }
</style>
